Overview
Sets the current video settings.

Note: Fields must be specified in pairs. For example, you cannot set only baseWidth without needing to specify baseHeight.

Request Fields
Name 
----:
fpsNumerator  >= 1{.datatype}
fpsDenominator  >= 1	{.datatype}
baseWidth  >= 1, <= 4096	{.datatype}
baseHeight  >= 1, <= 4096	{.datatype}
outputWidth  >= 1, <= 4096	{.datatype}
outputHeight  >= 1, <= 4096	{.datatype}

Overview
